{"tid":2298770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全台最愛自慰縣市是台東 ｢靠海多吃海鮮就是不一樣｣","createTime":"2020-11-24T09:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T11:12:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c385c1ea0efedce7e65eefc079d526080a15d3df","tid":2298770,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"國內頗具爭議的SWAG情色社群網站，今天（24日）公布1份關於台灣男性自慰習慣的調查，發現全台最愛自慰的縣市，竟然是台東縣的男性，每周次數竟高達7.2次；其次是金門，而台灣的中心南投縣，敬陪末座。對於這項調查結果，台東縣衛生局長黃明恩笑說，台東縣內衛生單位並未參與這份研究，不過自慰本屬正常性慾發洩行為，無需過度解讀。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201124/EUIDK5JD4NEMDCJLQ5HBRUZDTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201124%2FEUIDK5JD4NEMDCJLQ5HBRUZDTY%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=6ae7c5bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201124%2FEUIDK5JD4NEMDCJLQ5HBRUZDTY%2F&h=ef6adeda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201124/EUIDK5JD4NEMDCJLQ5HBRUZDTY/</a>"},{"pid":"86deee6ce53031aece26af5fec29c2278fa908e6","tid":2298770,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe979c35d7d714a7c67a3d2a596c4262ea741e9","tid":2298770,"uid":58254,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"相反，新北市人唔需要自慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9138fc2d0a35b159c39f063cb9de4581865d9d","tid":2298770,"uid":27664,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"香港後生仔：一周7.X 次會唔會太少"},{"pid":"ea58e09878c9480850f65765183308669c4e0ca9","tid":2298770,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86deee6ce53031aece26af5fec29c2278fa908e6","tid":2298770,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:31:11.000